articles.title: Why playing the national anthem at Anfield for King Charles' coronation could be an issue - CNN
articles.description: Liverpool has confirmed it will play "God Save the King'' ahead of its match against Brentford on Saturday to respect the coronation of King Charles III, despite the club admitting that many supporters hold "strong views" on the issue.
